mp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1333&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=9782c84adad3776dce2d3497c4e58e86 2000w"
                    />

                </a>
                            <h3 class="promo-series__name">
            <span class="a11y">Series: </span>
            <span class="promo-series__title">Zero Trust:</span>
                        <span class="promo-series__tagline">Inside Microsoft’s Cybersecurity Failures</span>
                    </h3>
    </div>
    
        <a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/zero-trust" class="promo-series__more-link">
        More in this series
        <div class="icon" style="transform: translateY(10%)">
            

