    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/telegram-terrorgram-collective-extremism-accelerationists-dallas-humber-matthew-allison">
                                    Neo-Nazi Telegram Users Panic Amid Crackdown and Arrest of Alleged Leaders of Online Extremist Group
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            An analysis by ProPublica and FRONTLINE shows a surge in activity on Telegram channels aligned with the Terrorgram Collective, as allies tried to rally support for their comrades in custody and sought to oust users they believed to be federal agents.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/ac-thompson">A.C. Thompson</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/james-bandler">James Bandler</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/brandon-roberts">Brandon Roberts</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-09-25EDT12:00">Sept. 25, 12 p.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
